entries.femaleVariant: Yo, V. Check it – there's a site on the Net out to smear the mayor, Weldon Holt. Well, acting mayor, 'cause y'know he's up for reelection or whatever.
Yeah, politics, am I right? Mud-slinging never stops – not for a minute.
Anyhow, my client wants that site sucked into the cold vacuum of cyberspace. Scan the brief if you need more info.
